'''Mandy Morton''' played [[Swilla Corey]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

She is credited by [[John Mollo]] as portraying one of two 'local girls' in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] as documented in the [[1979]] book [[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']].<ref name="TAoSW">[[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']] {{C|page 60}}</ref>

